          "type": "heading",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "PRIOR AUTHORIZATION CRITERIA",
          "id": "heading-1",
          "lang": null,
          "reading_order": null
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "BRAND NAME\n(generic)\n\nXYREM\n(sodium oxybate)\n\nStatus: CVS Caremark Criteria\nType: Initial Prior Authorization with Quantity Limit",
              "bold": true,
              "italic": false,
              "underline": false,
              "strikethrough": false,
              "superscript": false,
              "subscript": false,
              "code": false,
              "lang": null
            }
          ],
          "lang": null,
          "reading_order": null
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "POLICY",
          "id": "heading-2",
          "lang": null,
          "reading_order": null
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "FDA-APPROVED INDICATIONS",
          "id": "heading-3",
          "lang": null,
          "reading_order": null
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Xyrem is indicated for the treatment of cataplexy or excessive daytime sleepiness (EDS) in patients 7 years of age and older with narcolepsy.",
              "bold": false,
              "italic": false,
              "underline": false,
              "strikethrough": false,
              "superscript": false,
              "subscript": false,
              "code": false,
              "lang": null
            }
          ],
          "lang": null,
          "reading_order": null
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "COVERAGE CRITERIA",
          "id": "heading-4",
          "lang": null,
          "reading_order": null
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "The requested drug will be covered with prior authorization when the following criteria are met:",
              "bold": false,
              "italic": false,
              "underline": false,
              "strikethrough": false,
              "superscript": false,
              "subscript": false,
              "code": false,
              "lang": null
            }
          ],
          "lang": null,
          "reading_order": null
        },
        {
          "type": "list",
          "list_type": "unordered",
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "The request is for continuation of Xyrem (sodium oxybate)\nAND\no The requested drug is being prescribed for the treatment of cataplexy in narcolepsy in a patient 7 years of age or older\nAND\no The patient experienced a decrease in cataplexy episodes with narcolepsy\nOR\no The requested drug is being prescribed for the treatment of excessive daytime sleepiness in a patient 7 years of age or older with narcolepsy\nAND\no The patient experienced a decrease in daytime sleepiness with narcolepsy",
                  "bold": false,
                  "italic": false,
                  "underline": false,
                  "strikethrough": false,
                  "superscript": false,
                  "subscript": false,
                  "code": false,
                  "lang": null
                }
              ],
              "nested_list": null,
              "term": null,
              "definition": null
            }
          ],
          "reading_order": null
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "OR",
              "bold": true,
              "italic": false,
              "underline": false,
              "strikethrough": false,
              "superscript": false,
              "subscript": false,
              "code": false,
              "lang": null
            }
          ],
          "lang": null,
          "reading_order": null
        },
        {
          "type": "list",
          "list_type": "unordered",
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "The requested drug is being prescribed for the treatment of cataplexy in narcolepsy in a patient 7 years of age or older AND the diagnosis is confirmed by sleep lab evaluation",
                  "bold": false,
                  "italic": false,
                  "underline": false,
                  "strikethrough": false,
                  "superscript": false,
                  "subscript": false,
                  "code": false,
                  "lang": null
                }
              ],
              "nested_list": null,
              "term": null,
              "definition": null
            }
          ],
          "reading_order": null
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "OR",
              "bold": true,
              "italic": false,
              "underline": false,
              "strikethrough": false,
              "superscript": false,
              "subscript": false,
              "code": false,
              "lang": null
            }
          ],
          "lang": null,
          "reading_order": null
        },
        {
          "type": "list",
          "list_type": "unordered",
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "The requested drug is being prescribed for the treatment of excessive daytime sleepiness in a patient 7 years of age or older with narcolepsy AND the diagnosis is confirmed by sleep lab evaluation\nAND\no The patient has experienced an inadequate treatment response to at least one central nervous system (CNS) stimulant drug (e.g., amphetamine, dextroamphetamine, methylphenidate)\nOR\no The patient has experienced an intolerance to at least one central nervous system (CNS) stimulant drug (e.g., amphetamine, dextroamphetamine, methylphenidate)\nOR\no The patient has a contraindication that would prohibit a trial of central nervous system (CNS) stimulant drugs (e.g., amphetamine, dextroamphetamine, methylphenidate)\nAND\no If the patient is 18 years of age or older, the patient experienced an inadequate treatment response to armodafinil OR modafinil\nOR\no If the patient is 18 years of age or older, the patient experienced an intolerance to armodafinil OR modafinil\nOR\no If the patient is 18 years of age or older, the patient has a contraindication that would prohibit a trial of ALL of the following: A) armodafinil, B) modafinil",
                  "bold": false,
                  "italic": false,
                  "underline": false,
                  "strikethrough": false,
                  "superscript": false,
                  "subscript": false,
                  "code": false,
                  "lang": null
                }
              ],
              "nested_list": null,
              "term": null,
              "definition": null
            }
          ],
          "reading_order": null
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Quantity Limits Apply.\n540 mL/25 days or 1640 ml/75 days*\n*The duration of 25 days is used for a 30-day fill period and 75 days is used for a 90-day fill period to allow time for refill processing.",
              "bold": false,
              "italic": false,
              "underline": false,
              "strikethrough": false,
              "superscript": false,
              "subscript": false,
              "code": false,
              "lang": null
            }
          ],
          "lang": null,
          "reading_order": null
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "level": 3,
